div.p:
“Mañjuśrī, her rite is as follows. Mix together rotten rhododendron
              root, N and S read stag pa (“birch”) instead of stag ma (“rhododendron”). bugs born
            from manure, and two seeds. Insert them into a clay amulet, and recite this mantra:

gloss.term:
The fourth level of the heavens of the realm of desire, and
                the last stopping place of a buddha before his descent and reincarnation on earth;
                at present the abode of the future buddha Maitreya.
